{"tid":1524330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［901入機場］今日已恐襲，唔撚唔入機場哂冷下話？","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T02:41:26.000Z","uid":152341,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c97c74fe548c5426971248b86bcc4acce568a085","tid":1524330,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"佢老味啲狗已經玩恐襲<br />\n仲要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">老屈手足話佢地係黨鐵打人</span></strong><br />\n光明正大咁係黨鐵入面<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好似黑社會咁無差别打人</span></strong><br />\n仲要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔比急救員入站內救人</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一份憤怒我唔該每一位都同我記住佢之後901帶住佢同我塞爆個機場佢呀屌你</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvZD1Hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvZD1Hp.jpg&h=3b7bb479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6uAjt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6uAjt4.jpg&h=a671ed34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMHx585.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMHx585.jpg&h=9d81d784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQtNaAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQtNaAM.jpg&h=b84dfd53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afe85366e91b77368ee93b4cf516aadf649dac72","tid":1524330,"uid":152341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"96d8b3347e2e7fbd63bef9987d686bb